      "settings": {
        "eyebrow": "A history of",
        "heading": "Leading the industry",
        "description": "<p>StencilFast (formerly Pavement Stencil) began in our founder’s garage. Our commitment to quality and innovation got us into our bigger, more tech-equipped Roanoke, VA facilities a decade later. Those values continue to drive our work every single day.</p>",
